image_analysis.description: A high-end, elaborately decorated bedroom. The room features light-colored wallpaper with large blue floral patterns and shell-shaped wall sconces. A large, ornate blue glass chandelier hangs from the ceiling. The bed has a dark wood frame with a patterned headboard and white linens. Flanking the bed are two dark nightstands with matching lamps. In the foreground, there is a large, curved white upholstered chair or sofa. To the right, there is a tall black display cabinet with glass doors and a blue and white chevron-patterned curtain. The carpet is off-white with a blue grid pattern.

notes: The image is a photograph included in a document set, identified by the Bates stamp EFTA00000209.
